FBIS4-16535 "drsov074_e_94014" FBIS-SOV-94-074 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 UKRAINE International Affairs Swedish Citizen Expelled for Attempted `Nuclear Terrorism' Swedish Citizen Expelled for Attempted `Nuclear Terrorism' LD1504191094 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 1800 GMT 15 Apr 94 LD1504191094 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service Ukrainian BFN [Text] On 15 April Ukraine's Security Service expelled Swedish subject Erik Olaf Estenson, who was temporarily staying in Ukraine, beyond the borders of our state for intentions to carry out actions that can be qualified as international nuclear terrorism in relation to a foreign state. This has been reported by the Ukrainian Security Service press center.
